  "keyFeatures": [
    "Batch removal of Roblox badges with multi-threaded deletion",
    "Spam badge detection and inventory scanning",
    "MetaGamerScore integration for invalid game lists",
    "Multiple removal methods: by badge ID, place ID, user ID, group ID, or text file",
    "Badgers of Robloxia database support for disabled badges",
    "Safe token management via environment files"
